   <body class="- topic/body " xtrf="C:\Git\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\DITA-OT1.8.5\samples\diffed\_b-0-file-\COMMON\Appnotes\Application_Examples\trident_application_examples.xml" xtrc="body:1;16:32">
      <p class="- topic/p " status="unchanged" xtrf="C:\Git\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\DITA-OT1.8.5\samples\diffed\_b-0-file-\COMMON\Appnotes\Application_Examples\trident_application_examples.xml" xtrc="p:1;20:29">Switchtec can be used in many different system topologies. This section covers some common applications of the switches in various system environments. These are example configurations—not limitations of the device.</p>
